<h3>Dec( [address] );</h3>
<ul>
    <li>[address] - address to decrement</li>
</ul>


<h3>Description</h3>
<p>Decreases the value at the address by 1.  Creates an inc directive in assembler.</p>


<h3>Example</h3>

<code>
dec(^$d020);        // dec $d020 in assembler
dec(my_variable);   // dec my_variable
dec(my_array[i]);   // dec my_array,x
</code>
